text: Aerenea humerolineata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1980. It is known from Mexico.BioLib.cz - Aerenea humerolineata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Compsosomatini Category:Beetles described in 1980
